-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Site Page Order Helper Tool Install docs
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following assumes that you have a working and current Sakai trunk source 
installation.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For Sakai 2.2.x or 2.3.x
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See https://source.sakaiproject.org/contrib//asu/PageOrderHelper/branches/sakai_2-3-x/
instead. The version you are looking at now would require significant work to install
in older versions.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Get the code
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Add the pageorder helper to the top level of your Sakai source directory:
svn co https://source.sakaiproject.org/contrib/asu/PageOrderHelper/sakai/ PageOrderHelper

or

svn export https://source.sakaiproject.org/contrib/asu/PageOrderHelper/sakai/ PageOrderHelper


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
build and start Sakai as normal:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

maven sakai
....


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Use
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

From there whenever a user with update permissions on a site goes to SiteInfo
a link titled 'Page Order' will appear as the last item in the menu, clicking
on this link will take the user to this helper. From there most users should 
know what to do... and if not let me know as one of the main goals of this helper
is to be very easy to use.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Comments
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you have any comments or questions regarding this helper tool, please send
them to:

joshua.ryan@asu.edu


